\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img2.gifmagazine.net/gifmagazine/images/651133/original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.gifmagazine.net%2Fgifmagazine%2Fimages%2F651133%2Foriginal.gif&h=85ba23fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52efc665833593355755ce674735b992006ed86b","tid":196784,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你個手指公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a448af645d1abea1d66741775c63a86b55238687","tid":196784,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撻皮焗之前洗唔洗拮窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係因為同蛋漿一齊焗所以唔洗拮？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拮撻皮呢樣嘢，唔一定次次要做。要睇個餡係咩同埋係咪分開焗<br />\n好似呢個咁，餡係蛋漿，好似水咁稀，拮咗窿反而會令蛋漿滲入撻皮而整到個底淋patpat"},{"pid":"70728598ef8be7160336ec7264d09562b6c32bd8","tid":196784,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"成本幾錢隻？出面賣5$ on9"},{"pid":"a51d3050e20a6ff0fe958f9a8f9326b33b147d0e","tid":196784,"uid":39785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"好得意"},{"pid":"1baca4948f553488e38771438e440081cd4b004f","tid":196784,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:17:47.000Z","msg":"咁多野搞出去買好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537af72643ecef878840bc07ea8faee7a46c2052","tid":196784,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a5568bfc0373a99ddf53ebb2047f6211287ee5","tid":196784,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"睇到都覺得幾複雜下，冇勇氣氣試<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a5002b29959e3d910459835d87bb43f173ea75","tid":196784,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成本幾錢隻？出面賣5$ on9</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做成本撚好攰<br />\n自己整會用靚啲嘅材料，其實除返開都幾蚊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906da4b0d0090f6141ae4780318a76f7a3280126","tid":196784,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好得意</blockquote><br />\n多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2faf9f0f45aea19ae9a9513bd996742843aae619","tid":196784,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多野搞出去買好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n志在整果下開心，唔係志在慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbc40e3473fdf017e5cb7cb518671125083a926","tid":196784,"uid":8854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e05b0f1f95378f3593e736c42c2bb8d234a4d389","tid":196784,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbaby 做乜喊哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056e3bee265d60ad57fd95871ef8d95c79f330e2","tid":196784,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":